milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (392) involving teams Bermuda & Netherlands in ODIs
Romaine has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (16) for BMUDA, going past Mukuddem
Lionel Cann has broken the record for most sixes (14) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Dean Minors's 12
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (25) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
